    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate pot over a medium heat with your <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped ginger</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
