      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Roughly chop your <strong>roasted peanuts</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
