    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, fluff the <strong>cooked rice</strong> with a fork and add to a large bowl with your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix </strong>and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped herbs </strong>(save the rest for garnish!)</p><p>Add <strong>half </strong>the <strong>peanut dressing </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) to the bowl and toss – this is your<strong> rainbow salad</strong></p>",
