      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>rainbow salad</strong> and top with the <strong>roasted cauliflower florets</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>remaining peanut dressing </strong>and garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped herbs</strong>, <strong>chopped peanuts</strong> and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
